  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1704918702\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Chess Morph: The Queen's Wormholes</strong> is an original puzzle game inspired by chess. Control a lonely Queen with shapeshifting abilities and defeat the enemy army. <br>Move wisely, explore the wormholes on the board, take the enemy shape and kill them all.<br><br><strong>Take your enemy form to move like them</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/40d0f658e17de6b50a10e80242ca7421.poster.avif?t=1704918702\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/40d0f658e17de6b50a10e80242ca7421.webm?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/40d0f658e17de6b50a10e80242ca7421.mp4?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Use wormholes to reach different places</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/ca02a9087b2e32103387004304034a14.poster.avif?t=1704918702\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/ca02a9087b2e32103387004304034a14.webm?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/ca02a9087b2e32103387004304034a14.mp4?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Find the right path to kill them all</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/4800e5725925fab3b9418605b5286288.poster.avif?t=1704918702\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/4800e5725925fab3b9418605b5286288.webm?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209380/extras/4800e5725925fab3b9418605b5286288.mp4?t=1704918702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2>- Original puzzle game inspired by chess;<br>- Each piece move like the pieces in normal chess;<br>- 30+ <strong>hand-crafted levels</strong> with increasing difficulty;<br>- Make wise use of wormholes to get to the right place;<br>- Take the enemy shape and move like them;<br>- Relaxing soundtrack to help you keep the focus;",
